2 Days Ago A mini party was also held at the bride's family residence in Gwange 1 Ward, Malut Shuwa Street, Maiduguri.  A source close to Zainab told SaharaReporters that the Senate President gifted her N100 million a few days after they were introduced to each other. See Also






