1 Day Ago The bride was said to have bought three houses in Maiduguri out of the money.  Speaking to SaharaReporters on Monday, the source added that Zainab has arrived at a multi-million naira mansion in Abuja.  “She is now here in Abuja staying in a mansion provided by Senate President. She is staying at Maitama. And even the people that attended the ceremony that held on Sunday at her new house, received N100, 000 each from Lawan as a gift. More than 50 women's attended the ceremony today,” the source said.  A text message sent to Ola Awoniyi, Special Adviser on Media to the Senate President was not replied to.